#. <section class="sutta" id="sn20.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga"
msgstr "1. Similes"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Siṅgālasutta → sigālasuttaṃ (bj) | siṅgālaka 1 (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn20.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Siṅgālasutta"
msgstr "11. A Jackal"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli2.272"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Assuttha no tumhe, bhikkhave, rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ jarasiṅgālassa "
"vassamānassā”ti?"
msgstr "“Mendicants, did you hear an old jackal howling at the crack of dawn?”"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.4"
msgid "“Eso kho, bhikkhave, jarasiṅgālo ukkaṇḍakena nāma rogajātena phuṭṭho."
msgstr "“That old jackal has the disease called mange."

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.5"
msgid "So yena yena icchati tena tena gacchati;"
msgstr "Yet it still goes where it wants,"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.6"
msgid "yattha yattha icchati tattha tattha tiṭṭhati;"
msgstr "stands where it wants,"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.7"
msgid "yattha yattha icchati tattha tattha nisīdati;"
msgstr "sits where it wants,"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.8"
msgid "yattha yattha icchati tattha tattha nipajjati;"
msgstr "and lies down where it wants."

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.9"
msgid "sītakopi naṃ vāto upavāyati."
msgstr "And the cool breeze still blows on it."

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.10"
msgid ""
"Sādhu khvassa, bhikkhave, yaṃ idhekacco sakyaputtiyapaṭiñño evarūpampi "
"attabhāvapaṭilābhaṃ paṭisaṃvediyetha."
msgstr ""
"A certain person here who claims to be a follower of the Sakyan son would be "
"lucky to experience even such an incarnation."

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.11"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.12"
msgid "‘appamattā viharissāmā’ti."
msgstr "‘We will stay diligent.’"

msgctxt "sn20.11:1.13"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.11:1.14"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
